### World Storage API Tests

# Get all stored worlds
GET {{baseUrl}}/World
Accept: application/json

###

# Get a specific world by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/World/sample-world-id
Accept: application/json

###

# Generate and automatically save a new world
POST {{baseUrl}}/World/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "worldName": "Test Fantasy World",
  "theme": "Fantasy-SciFi",
  "techLevel": 6,
  "magicLevel": 8
}

###

# Generate a complete world (automatically saved)
POST {{baseUrl}}/World/generate-complete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "worldName": "Complete Test World",
  "theme": "Cyberpunk-Fantasy",
  "techLevel": 9,
  "magicLevel": 6,
  "totalPlaces": 25,
  "continentCount": 2,
  "countryCount": 4,
